{"tid":1012952,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我讀環保，覺得而家啲走塑撚真係多鳩餘","createTime":"2019-02-08T03:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T08:26:05.000Z","uid":105802,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b14482c34b235d3f41584cbf794c3ed298975bb4","tid":1012952,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:41:12.000Z","msg":"我係唔會話佢地係環保撚<br />\n個個都剩係識得走塑<br />\n點解？<br />\n簡單囉<br />\n易做囉<br />\n你試下叫佢地夏天唔開冷氣？唔好搭的士？<br />\n<br />\n根本而家啲所謂要環保既人都多鳩餘<br />\n你走塑係人地做多左野<br />\n又唔係你做多左野<br />\n又話要保護海洋生物<br />\n而家就係因為全球暖化<br />\n啲北極熊仲瘦過非洲兒童<br />\n保護動物？<br />\n收皮啦撚樣<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"e978a221805311ec5cf2bd1b95be3f8a5438feb9","tid":1012952,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"駁5刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388e290cd99c795c3827593efd18d0e47c385a31","tid":1012952,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"讀環保都多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55b2321ea4b35d2a69bdd6378c9c03830342e89","tid":1012952,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主，下次又可以串鳩環保撚開冷氣"},{"pid":"dc17cdbf21d419a9275dbc012f76bc9f9ae5f79b","tid":1012952,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f55b2321ea4b35d2a69bdd6378c9c03830342e89","tid":1012952,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主，下次又可以串鳩環保撚開冷氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"仲要全屋都開哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526e58d8d830d9f89d1d2d4f187a5499ddab65f3","tid":1012952,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:57:02.000Z","msg"